<paragraph id="IFRS16_B57" base="F45930820"><paranum>B57</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRSÂ 16"/><data name="paranum" value="B57"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS16_P0596">For a <xref base="F45929685" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0363">lease<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0214"/></ph></xref> of land and buildings in which the amount for the land element is immaterial to the lease, a <xref base="F45929747" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0382">lessor<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0222"/></ph></xref> may treat the land and buildings as a single unit for the purpose of lease classification and classify it as a <xref base="SL45930039" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0354">finance lease<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0122"/></ph></xref> or an <xref base="F45929764" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0384">operating lease<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0269"/></ph></xref> applying <xref id="IFRS16_X0468" base="F47961327" href="IFRS16_62.dita#IFRS16_62">paragraphs 62&#x2013;66</xref> and <xref id="IFRS16_X0469" base="F47961328" href="IFRS16_gB53-B58.dita#IFRS16_gB53-B58/IFRS16_gB53-B58_TI">B53&#x2013;B54</xref>. In such a case, a lessor shall regard the <xref base="F45929638" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0350">economic life<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0094"/></ph></xref> of the buildings as the economic life of the entire <xref base="F45929849" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0392">underlying asset<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0373"/></ph></xref>.</p></body></paragraph>